kehilangan awak
daripada kehilangan peluang...

4
00:00:22,343 --> 00:00:25,250
dalam industri ini,
hanya kerana skandal.

5
00:00:25,772 --> 00:00:27,124
Jadi...

6
00:00:29,294 --> 00:00:31,164
mari mulakan semula.

7
00:00:36,509 --> 00:00:38,983
Awak masih mahu melepaskan saya?

8
00:00:43,143 --> 00:00:44,582
Jika awak lepaskan sekarang,

9
00:00:46,549 --> 00:00:47,896
kita takkan...

10
