berjumpa satu sama lain lagi.

11
00:01:12,366 --> 00:01:13,790
Cik Oh Jin Sim.

12
00:01:23,383 --> 00:01:24,725
Saya cintakan awak.

13
00:01:58,571 --> 00:02:00,403
(Episod 15)

14
